        <item>
            <title>Samsung 横滨设晶片研发基地，将获日本政府拨款支助</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/22/samsung-set-up-chip-packaging-research-facility-japan/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-set-up-chip-packaging-research-facility-japan</link>
